Package com.isti.traceview.commands

Class Summary
LoadDataCommand This command loads raw data into data providers from sources discovered on the parse stage
MeanCommand This command changes mean mode
OffsetCommand This command changes offset mode
OverlayCommand This command changes overlay mode
RotateCommand This command performs rotation
SaveAllDataCommand This command dumps all loaded data into temporary storage area
SelectCommand This command selects choosed channels, i.e hides all unchoosed channels on graph panel
SelectTimeCommand This command selects time range, i.e sets desired time range to graph panel
SelectValueCommand This command selects values range, i.e sets desired range of Y values on axis
SetScaleModeCommand This command sets desired scale mode for graph panel
